  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a half board basis, breakfast and dinner is served each day. Drinks are not included.</p>
<p>Each morning a continental buffet breakfast with a range of hot options is served between 7 and 10am.</p>
<p>Evening meals are taken in the hotels main restaurant where they will provide you with several time slots so you can reserve your table. Each evening you will be served a three course a la carte evening meal with choice of menu. This will include a starter, choice of main course and a dessert or a cheese course.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>
<p>Earlier meal times are available for children, this is usually at 7pm.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
