  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic twin rooms</strong> sleep two to three people and are around 20m². The room is made up as a twin or double and has an additional single bed which suitable for children up to 11 years old.</p>
<p><strong>Family quad room</strong> are around 25m² and sleep two adults and two children.  The rooms are made up as a double or twin beds with an additional bed for one or two children up to 11 years old.</p>
<p>Single occupancy rooms are available on request, please give our reservations team a call to book this room type.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Toiletries </li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities </li>
<li>Satellite/cable flat screen TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Mini bar</li>
<li>Bed linen and towels </li>
<li>Alarm clock on request </li>
<li>Daily house keeping is included</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
